<br />
 :!: Spell Idea  :!: 
<br />

<br />
Level 64- Elemental Destruction. Mana-700 - Cast time- 9.0
<br />
  Hits mob for 700 and 200 every 6 seconds for 0:36. Lure based and snares mob.
<br />

<br />
Level 69- Elemental Chaos. Mana-900 - Cast time- 9.0
<br />
  Hits mob for 900 and 250 every 6 seconds for 0:36. Lure based and snares mob. (Projected idea, assuming the nuke is pretty big making this big to balance).<br />_________________<br />Quote of the month- "I'd HIGHLY suggest you not call me a retard, buddy. I played on Legends for a couple months and am far from a retard. You WILL NOT get another warning for personal attacks, Cubis." -The evil admin
