			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I was exaggerating to make a point.  Yes, I know we won't be using our rains to quad kite, I mentioned that.  But we won't be kiting like a necro either.  We don't have all the horrible nasty DoTs that a necro has.  We can't FD, our PET can't FD, in case something goes wrong.  We can't root to give ourselves med time.  We can't harmshield (unless you have a Duennan Shielding ring) to give us another buffer if the mob catches us for a quick swipe.  We can't lifetap to heal any little damage that we do manage to get.
<br />

<br />
A short duration snare might be "convenient", but honestly, I think our solutions to our soloing issues shouldn't come from making us closer to other classes in abilities.  We should have our OWN tactics and playstyles based around our pets, and not just as another source of damage like a necro pet.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=96985" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fazzadien Elementweaver</a> 
