That's rogue, rogue, wizard, rogue, wizard, mage, mage. Pretty typical, unless there are more rogues and wizards at a raid than just 5. =p Any numbers you get are going to vary depending on what's being killed and the relative gear of those killing it, who is and isn't lazy, etc... but Rogues and Wizards are generally going to top damage lists, whatever the situation. 
